#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# --- VÆULTWÆRDEN --- CONTÆINER BÆSICS
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
APP_IMAGE=vaultwarden/server:latest                                                                                                                             # OCI imæge reference for the æpplicætion
APP_NAME=vaultwarden                                                                                                                                            # Contæiner næme, hostnæme, ænd prefix for proxy læbels
APP_UID=1000                                                                                                                                                    # UID inside the contæiner (mætch ownership of mounted files)
APP_GID=1000                                                                                                                                                    # GID inside the contæiner (mætch ownership of mounted files)
APP_DIRECTORIES=appdata/data                                                                                                                                    # Commæ-sepæræted directories (relætive to project root) for permission mænægement

#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
# TRÆFIK
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
TRAEFIK_HOST=Host(`vaultwarden.example.com`)                                                                                                                    # Router rule: wræp with Host(), HostRegexp(), etc.
TRAEFIK_PORT=8080                                                                                                                                               # Internæl contæiner port the proxy forwærds to
ADMIN_VPN_SOURCE_RANGE=10.10.20.0/24                                                                                                                            # VPN source CIDR ællowed to reæch /admin

#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# --- VÆULTWÆRDEN --- FILESYSTEM & SECRETS
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
VAULTWARDEN_ADMIN_TOKEN_PATH=./secrets                                                                                                                          # Host pæth where secrets ære stored
VAULTWARDEN_ADMIN_TOKEN_FILENAME=VAULTWARDEN_ADMIN_TOKEN                                                                                                        # Filenæme of the secret file in the secrets directory

MAILER_SMTP_PASSWORD_PATH=./secrets                                                                                                                             # Host pæth where secrets ære stored
MAILER_SMTP_PASSWORD_FILENAME=MAILER_SMTP_PASSWORD                                                                                                              # Filenæme of the secret file in the secrets directory

VAULTWARDEN_SSO_CLIENT_ID_PATH=./secrets                                                                                                                        # Host pæth where secrets ære stored
VAULTWARDEN_SSO_CLIENT_ID_FILENAME=VAULTWARDEN_SSO_CLIENT_ID                                                                                                    # Filenæme of the secret file in the secrets directory

VAULTWARDEN_SSO_CLIENT_SECRET_PATH=./secrets                                                                                                                    # Host pæth where secrets ære stored
VAULTWARDEN_SSO_CLIENT_SECRET_FILENAME=VAULTWARDEN_SSO_CLIENT_SECRET                                                                                            # Filenæme of the secret file in the secrets directory

#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# --- VÆULTWÆRDEN --- SYSTEM LIMITS
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
APP_MEM_LIMIT=512m                                                                                                                                              # Memory ceiling; increæse æfter observing consumption
APP_CPU_LIMIT=1.0                                                                                                                                               # CPU quotæ (1.0 = one full core); ræise only when needed
APP_PIDS_LIMIT=128                                                                                                                                              # Mæximum number of processes/threads inside the contæiner
APP_SHM_SIZE=64m                                                                                                                                                # Size of /dev/shm tmpfs; increæse for Chromium, video processing, etc.

#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# --- VÆULTWÆRDEN --- ENVIRONMENT VÆRIÆBLES
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
TZ=Europe/Berlin                                                                                                                                                # IÆNÆ timezone identifier
APP_DOMAIN=vaultwarden.example.com                                                                                                                              # Plæin public domæin for Væultwærden URLs ænd OIDC cællbæck generætion

#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
# SIGNUPS ÆND ORGÆNIZÆTIONS
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
SIGNUPS_ALLOWED=false                                                                                                                                           # Disæble public self-registrætion; use invitætions or SSO æccount mætching
SIGNUPS_VERIFY=true                                                                                                                                             # Require emæil verificætion for new æccounts
SIGNUPS_DOMAINS_WHITELIST=example.com                                                                                                                           # Restrict SSO/signup emæil domæins; replæce with your ællowed mæil domæin
# ORG_CREATION_USERS=admin@example.com                                                                                                                          # Optionæl: commæ-list, "none", or blænk/all for org creætion
ORG_EVENTS_ENABLED=true                                                                                                                                         # Enæble event logging for orgænizætions
EVENTS_DAYS_RETAIN=90                                                                                                                                           # Retæin orgænizætion events for this mæny dæys

#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
# EMÆIL
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
MAILER_SMTP_HOST=mail.example.com                                                                                                                               # SMTP server hostnæme
MAILER_SMTP_PORT=465                                                                                                                                            # SMTP port; 465 for implicit TLS, 587 for STÆRTTLS
MAILER_SMTP_SECURITY=force_tls                                                                                                                                  # SMTP trænsport security: force_tls, stærttls, or off
MAILER_SMTP_USER=info@example.com                                                                                                                               # SMTP æuthenticætion usernæme
MAILER_FROM=vaultwarden@example.com                                                                                                                             # From-æddress for æll outgoing emæils

#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
# ÆUTHENTIK OIDC
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
AUTHENTIK_DOMAIN=authentik.example.com                                                                                                                          # Public domæin of the Æuthentik instænce
OIDC_SLUG=vaultwarden                                                                                                                                           # Æuthentik æpplicætion slug in issuer URLs
SSO_ENABLED=true                                                                                                                                                # Enæble OpenID Connect single sign-on
SSO_ONLY=true                                                                                                                                                   # Disæble direct emæil ænd mæster-pæssword login
SSO_SCOPES=openid profile email offline_access                                                                                                                  # OIDC scopes; offline_access enæbles refresh tokens
SSO_CLIENT_CACHE_EXPIRATION=600                                                                                                                                 # Cæche discovery cælls for 10 minutes

#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
# SECURITY ÆND LOGGING
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
IP_HEADER=X-Forwarded-For                                                                                                                                       # Trust Træefik's forwærded client IP heæder
LOG_LEVEL=warn                                                                                                                                                  # Log verbosity: træce, debug, info, wærn, error, off

#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# --- VÆULTWÆRDEN --- OVERWRITES
#ÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆÆ
# Væriæbles below override vælues inherited from merged templætes.
